roller into UserAccountService, making the\ncontroller thin delegates with a single dependency and the update flow\na single transaction. Share the new-password validation and the\nrecovery-lockout helper between the reset and update flows instead of\nduplicating them.\n\nReplace the second bcrypt verification in the new==old guard with plain\nstring equality (the old password is already verified against the\nstored hash), and spend one bcrypt verification on the unknown-username\npath so the generic error is not undermined by a timing side-channel.\n\nFold the single-test AuthUpdatePasswordPermitAllTest into\nAuthenticationControllerTest and add unit tests for updateExpiredPassword\ncovering the timing burn and guard ordering, which are only observable\nwith mocks.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"d29fe7c96378a8b6ee8e92e2d54f42186d44d381","tree_id":"a87e6b258763e6a135e59e31e04e4891d34e3570","timestamp":"2026-07-04T18:47:29Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.gith